Harris Pastides - Wikipedia






















 






Harris Pastides

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Harris Pastides








President of the University of S. Carolina



Incumbent



Assumed office
August 1, 2008


Preceded by
Andrew A. Sorenson





Personal details


