Harris Pastides: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 6:02 PM ET
Diversified Consumer Services

Company Overview of University of South Carolina



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Harris   Pastides  President, University of South CarolinaAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships63--
Background

		Dr. Harris Pastides has been the President of The University of South Carolina Columbia, SC., since August 1, 2008. Dr. Pastides served as a decade of service as a Professor, Dean and Vice President at South Carolina Columbia. Under his leadership as Vice President for Research and Health Sciences, research funding and sponsored programs at South Carolina have increased 89 percent since 2002, reaching a record $206 million for fiscal year 2008. He continues to take a ... leading role in the development of Innovista, the research innovation district he helped design and launch during his tenure. With Focus Carolina, one of his first major initiatives as University president, he has launched the most comprehensive strategic planning initiative in the University's history. Before joining the South Carolina faculty, he was a Professor of Epidemiology and Chairman of the Department of Biostatistics and Epidemiology at the University of Massachusetts at Amherst. He has been an Independent Director of Synovus Financial Corporation since April 24, 2014. He serves as a Trustee of South Carolina Research Authority. He served as a Director of The National Bank of South Carolina. Dr. Pastides received his Master's of Public Health and a Ph.D. in Epidemiology from Yale University.Read Full Background




